      <title>投资者支撑南非至关重要的南非议会预算投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/south-african-budget-vote-set-to</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非议会将对联合政府之间的谈判地位的不确定性进行不确定性，以解决他们在支出计划上的差异，这将在一项关键的预算立法上进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/south-african-budget-vote-set-to</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 07:06:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SCMP说，XI突然互换了两个政治局成员的工作。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/xi-abruptly-swaps-jobs-of-two-politburo-members-scmp-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据《南中国晨邮报》的报道，中国统治的共产党突然改变了两名政治局成员的角色，这是史无前例的举动，这是习近平在他的第三任期内的人事规范而发生的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/xi-abruptly-swaps-jobs-of-two-politburo-members-scmp-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 06:06:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚雇用壳牌部门的前首席执行官领导国家石油公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/nigeria-hires-ex-ceo-of-shell-unit-to-lead-state-oil-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂诺布（Bola Tinubu）任命了壳牌公司的前任负责人，负责经营国家石油公司，这是非洲最大的原油生产商，旨在提高产出和恢复当地的炼油能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/nigeria-hires-ex-ceo-of-shell-unit-to-lead-state-oil-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 05:33:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南，随着关税织机的关税，派遣副总理在美国最后一刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-races-to-minimize-trump-tariffs-sends-deputy-pm-on-last-minute-us-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南计划在本周末将另一个顶级官员和商业代表团派往美国，这表明唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）推出互惠关税的世界括号是激烈的幕后活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-races-to-minimize-trump-tariffs-sends-deputy-pm-on-last-minute-us-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 05:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国吹捧贸易福利在最后一条关税上诉中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-touts-trade-benefits-for-us-in-last-ditch-tariff-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国强调了美国的农民和科技公司在执政的共产党的官方报纸上是经济关系的受益者，这显然吸引了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）预计宣布新的全球关税的前夕，呼吁较大的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-touts-trade-benefits-for-us-in-last-ditch-tariff-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 05:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普削弱中国海上重量的出价可能需要“数十年”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-s-bid-to-weaken-china-s-maritime-heft-may-take-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据洛杉矶港口负责人的说法，特朗普政府计划挑战中国海上统治权，并通过造船业的变化迎来迎接中国的统治地位，这可能是数十年的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-s-bid-to-weaken-china-s-maritime-heft-may-take-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 05:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列扩大针对加沙哈马斯的地面行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/israel-expands-ground-operations-in-gaza-in-push-against-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列表示，它正在加沙的军事行动扩大，几天后，在要求巴勒斯坦领土南部的人们离开时，它为与哈马斯的战斗做准备时要离开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/israel-expands-ground-operations-in-gaza-in-push-against-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 04:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在特朗普的佛罗里达选秀权避免烦恼时在威斯康星州斥责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/musk-backed-candidate-defeated-in-wisconsin-supreme-court-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的候选人在威斯康星州的司法竞赛中遭受了巨大的损失，尽管世界上最富有的人向竞选活动投入了数百万美元，而共和党人则避免在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）家乡佛罗里达州的两个关键的美国众议院席位中感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/musk-backed-candidate-defeated-in-wisconsin-supreme-court-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 02:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国模拟台湾演习第二天的港口罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-holds-second-day-of-exercises-near-taiwan-squeezing-lai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周三在台湾周围进行了第二天的演习，这加剧了它对赖斯总统的前所未有的军事压力，它非常不喜欢它。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-holds-second-day-of-exercises-near-taiwan-squeezing-lai</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:44:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
